 national chemical in the most ambitious foreign takeover attempt by a chinese company to date here are five things to know about the company commonly known as chemchina  feb  am by wayne ma  what is chemchina share on twitter china national chemical corp was formed in  and is the largest chemicals company in china headquartered in beijing chemchina remains unlisted and is a stateowned enterprise ultimately managed by the chinese government chemchina’s revenue last year was  billion and it employs  people according to its website  the number of people chemchina says it employs  what does it do share on twitter chemchina produces a wide array of chemicals and is also a leading manufacturer of tires conveyor belts and chemical machinery the company is china’s largest producer of pesticides and its chief mandate is to improve the protection of chinese crops the company operates nine crudeoil refineries in china but also owns the popular malan noodle fastfood restaurant chain  who leads the company share on twitter chemchina’s founder and chairman is yearold ren jianxin mr ren was born in northwestern china studied chemical engineering and has a graduate degree in economics he founded his first company bluestar in  with loan of less than  and presided over its expansion from an industrialcleaning company to a chemicals conglomerate acquiring more than  stateowned chinese chemicals companies it later merged with other businesses affiliated with china’s chemicals ministry and mr ren was named head of the stateowned behemoth agence francepressegetty images  what has the company been buying share on twitter since  chemchina has spent billions of dollars on overseas acquisitions in countries including france italy germany israel and the uk its more notable acquisitions include italian tire maker pirelli which it bought for about  billion last year and israel’s makhteshim agan group the world’s largest maker of generic pesticides for about  billion in  other acquisitions include france’s adisseo group and rhodia makers of animal feed and organic silicon respectively and kraussmaffei group a german company that makes equipment to process plastics and rubber getty images  why does it want syngenta share on twitter chemchina says it wants to grow syngenta’s business in china and other emerging markets but it may also have an eye on the pesticide and seed giant’s significant foothold in the us acquiring syngenta’s intellectual property is also attractive as the swiss company develops genetically engineered seeds that may help further open the tightlyregulated chinese market for biotech crops agence francepressegetty images more  things china national chemical corporation private company information  bloomberg july    am et chemicals company overview of china national chemical corporation snapshot people company overview china national chemical corporation through its subsidiaries manufactures chemical products the company offers chemical materials and specialty chemical products that include organosilicon silicon alloy organofluorine polyurethane and engineering plastics as well as high performance fibers general plastics and rubbers and animal nutrition chemical products it also provides basic chemical products that comprise salt and coal chemicals minerals and mineral basic chemicals oil processing and refining products such as energy and petrochemical products agrochemicals which include chemical fertilizers and pesticides and rubber products including auto tire nontire rubber spe china national chemical corporation through its subsidiaries manufactures chemical products the company offers chemical materials and specialty chemical products that include organosilicon silicon alloy organofluorine polyurethane and engineering plastics as well as high performance fibers general plastics and rubbers and animal nutrition chemical products it also provides basic chemical products that comprise salt and coal chemicals minerals and mineral basic chemicals oil processing and refining products such as energy and petrochemical products agrochemicals which include chemical fertilizers and pesticides and rubber products including auto tire nontire rubber special tire and latex products in addition the company offers chemical equipment that include ionic membrane electrolyzers rubber machinery drying equipment and axle gears and consulting services it serves customers in china and internationally china national chemical corporation is based in beijing china detailed description  beisihuan xiluhaidian districtbeijing  china phone     wwwchemchinacomcn key executives for china national chemical corporation mr jianxin ren chairman president and general manager age  mr zhihong lei deputy general manager age  mr yinhai wan deputy general manager fan xiaosen deputy general manager zhou lewen deputy general manager compensation as of fiscal year  china national chemical corporation key developments nufarm races sumitomo for chemchina assets jul   nufarm limited asxnuf is believed to be closing in on a  million portfolio of china national chemical corporations chemchina protection assets according to sources in a sales process where the listed australian agrochemicals operation is going head to head with its major shareholder sumitomo chemical company limited tse a dataroom is understood to have been opened by chemchina for the sale of assets within its subsidiary adama agricultural solutions ltd federal trade commission approves final order with china national chemical corporation and syngenta ag preserving competition in us markets for three pesticides jun   federal trade commission has approved a final order settling charges that the proposed merger of china national chemical corporation chemchina and syngenta ag would harm competition in the us markets for the herbicide paraquat the insecticide abamectin and the fungicide chlorothalonil first announced in april  the complaint alleged that without the proposed divestiture the merger would eliminate the direct competition that exists between chemchina generics subsidiary adama and syngentas branded products the merger would also increase the likelihood that us customers buying paraquat abamectin and chlorothalonil would be forced to pay higher prices or accept reduced service for these products the complaint states eurochem group ag and china national chemical corporation consider starting joint production in russia jun   eurochem group ag announced the signing of a memorandum of intent memorandum with china national chemical corporation chemchina for a potential partnership to jointly produce industrial products in russia the project both companies agreed to form a working group to further evaluate the technical feasibility of the project and will carry out due diligence under the memorandum eurochem and chemchina consider jointly starting production of industrial products specifically propylene oxide propylene glycol and polyols and isocyanate mditdi the former has vast application across many industries including for the development of synthetic lubricants surfactants and polyurethane products with the latter mainly used for thermal insulation in construction this will be the first production of its kind for russia and the cis which currently rely on imports from germany the benelux countries the us and japan future output is expected to be sold predominantly in russia to meet growing internal demand if it goes ahead the project will be implemented at eurochems novomoskovskiy azot plant in the tula region russia this will allow eurochem to optimise current production capacity at this facility by integrating the additional downstream production process which will utilize existing byproducts and infrastructure chemchina will deliver the necessary production technology similar private companies by industry company name region d carbon graphene material co ltd asia aladdin shanghai biochemical technology co ltd asia alar xinhongfa